{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":11,"day":15}],"page_start":2,"page_end":2,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席和我们在一起","authors":["北京部队学习毛主席著作积极分子代表大会代表","赵宝生"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢声雷动震天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日心中升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光照亮千万里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写信告诉父母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫农后代见到了大救星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席恩情比天大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“万岁万岁毛主席！”喊了千声又万声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写信告诉工人老大哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席身体非常好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命人民最幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海航行有依靠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写信告诉革命师生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席对咱笑盈盈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限希望，无限关怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教育革命要敢闯敢冲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写信告诉老战友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席对咱招了手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命形势无限好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗私批修，咱毛主席的战士要永当红旗手。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"教育革命","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}